title: Iowa Students Can’t Afford Rand Paul’s Policies (Iowa Democratic Party)
text: ( Source : Iowa Democratic Party ) Paul would endanger Pell Grants used by 111 , 000 Iowa Students DES MOINES-Rand Paul will embark on his tour of 11 Iowa college campuses this week, hoping Iowa college students will save his fledging campaign.
